OL,3,CWhat it's like living with
OL,4,C'debilitating' locked-in syndrome
OL,6,F"The immediate reaction people have is
OL,7,F'oh my god, he can't move at all. He
OL,8,Fcan't do this or do that.' The trials
OL,9,Fand tribulations I have endured are
OL,10,Funbelievable."
OL,12,FHoward founded the Locked-in Trust in
OL,13,FOctober 2020, to help other people
OL,14,Fwith similar conditions live life to
OL,15,Fits fullest potential.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
