OL,3,CWhat it's like living with
OL,4,C'debilitating' locked-in syndrome
OL,6,F"The book concludes with my transition
OL,7,Ffrom the hospital setting to community
OL,8,Flife. This book allows everyone to
OL,9,Fjoin me on my miraculous journey.
OL,11,F"I hope my book lifts the mood of
OL,12,Fpeople around the globe, there is
OL,13,Falways hope, no matter the
OL,14,Fcircumstances."
OL,16,F"I recently signed an agreement with
OL,17,FTellwell to distribute my book to over
OL,18,F40,000 book retailers worldwide," he
OL,19,Fadded.
