OL,3,CWhat it's like living with
OL,4,C'debilitating' locked-in syndrome
OL,6,FHoward has many plans for the future,
OL,7,Fnot least writing another two books -
OL,8,Fmaking a trilogy.
OL,10,F"'Hope, Love and Glory' was the
OL,11,Foriginal title of my book, but because
OL,12,Fthe duration of my recovery is
OL,13,Fextending into a lifetime, I've
OL,14,Fdivided the original title into three
OL,15,Fparts.
OL,17,F"It's going to be a very busy future
OL,18,Findeed," Howard said.
